Southern California Gas Company - Wikipedia






















 






Southern California Gas Company

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






This article relies too much on references to primary sources. Please improve this by adding secondary or tertiary sources. (November 2006) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)



SoCalGas









Type

Subsidiary


Industry
Utilities


