	Additional help for customers with major health concerns.


                      See if You Qualify     
                    












These programs are funded by California utility customers and administered by SoCalGas under the auspices of the California Public Utilities Commission. Program funds will be allocated on a first-come, first-served basis until such funds are no longer available. A program may be modified or terminated without prior notice. Eligibility requirements apply; see the program conditions for details.




























