Pay Bill
Ways to Pay







Ways to Pay





We offer a number of different ways to pay your bill. Find the one that's right for you.


















Pay with My Account

	View and pay your bill online through our secure site at no charge.

	Benefits of My Account



			Schedule email bill reminders

			Get your account balance

			Pay by text

			Schedule automatic payments



	Pay with: Checking or Savings Account
	 



Pay Now



















Pay by Credit or Debit

	Credit or debit card payments are handled through BillMatrix, an independent service provider.

	Payments Accepted


		MasterCard and Visa credit cards

		Debit/ATM - NYCE, PULSE, ACCEL, STAR

		Electronic Checks


	Note: $1.50 BillMatrix convenience fee

	Pay with: Credit or Debit Card
	 



Pay Now


              
                
                  Or call 1-800-232-6629 to pay by phone with BillMatrix
                
                
              
            

















Pay by Home Banking

	If you pay your bills at an online payment site such as a bank, credit union, brokerage firm or other financial institution, you can receive your bill electronically.

	To find out if your financial institution offers e-bills from SoCalGas,
  

  
    
   

  
    
  

  
    
    
      
        Fiserv's e-bill site       
        
          

    
  
  
. If you don't see your financial institution on the list please contact them.

	 

	Pay with: Checking or Savings Account










Pay by Phone

	Once you're enrolled in Pay by Phone, simply call our toll-free number to authorize a payment from your checking account at no charge.
	
		 

Download and print an application  or call 1-800-427-2200 to receive an application by mail.

		 

		Pay with: Checking or Savings Account


	 










Pay in Person
To pay your bill in person, search for a company branch office or authorized payment location near you.


        Find a Payment Location       
                
      

Most Authorized Payment Locations accept cash, checks, money orders and cashier's checks as forms of payment. Walmart and Kmart stores accept cash and PIN-based debit cards.










Pay by Mail

	To pay your bill by mail, simply mail your check with your bill stub to:

	SoCalGas
	P.O. Box C
	Monterey Park, CA 91756

	Pay with: Check or Money Order










Pay by Direct Debit

	Once you register for Direct Debit, your monthly payment is automatically deducted from your checking or savings account at no charge.

Download and print an application   or call 1-800-427-2200 to receive an application by mail.

	Pay with: Checking or Savings Account










Level Pay Plan
Smooth out the ups and downs of your monthly gas bill by averaging annual gas consumption and costs over a 12-month period.


        Learn More       
                
      

For help remembering to pay your gas bill each month, sign up for Third-Party Bill Notification.


























