Southern California Gas Company (SoCalGas®) customers can now order energy-saving products from Energy Federation Incorporated (EFI), an authorized contractor of SoCalGas. Customers will be required to enter certain customer information, including customer's SoCalGas account number to place an order and by providing such information, authorize EFI and SoCalGas to use such information for purposes of conducting the rebate program. Rebates are available on a first-come, first-served basis until program funds are no longer available. Purchase limits and delivery restrictions apply. The rebate program is funded by California utility customers and administered by SoCalGas, under the auspices of the California Public Utilities Commission (CPUC).

Energy Federation, Inc. Southborough Massachusetts USA
866-807-1317, customerservice@efi.org
© 2017 Energy Federation, Inc.











Microsoft personalized ad preferences




 













To opt out of personalized ads in this browser, your browser history must allow first-party and third-party cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to NOT delete browsing history on exit. Instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings, privacy, or help documentation.

















